Package: covHeavyTail
Title: Mean and Covariance Matrix Estimation under Heavy Tails
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Daniel P. Palomar <daniel.p.palomar@gmail.com> [aut, cre],
    Junyan LIU <liubl@connect.ust.hk> [aut]
Maintainer: Daniel P. Palomar <daniel.p.palomar@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides several functions to estimate the mean 
    and covariance matrix for multivariate iid time-series under heavy-tailed 
    distributions commonly arising in financial data.
URL: http://www.danielppalomar.com/
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
License: GPL-3 | file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: Gmedian,
    stats
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
